name: TenYearProbabilityOfAllMajorOsteoporosisRelatedFracture
title: Ten-year probability of all major osteoporosis related fracture
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent a ten-year probability of all major osteoporosis-related fracture as determined by the Fracture Risk Assessment Tool (FRAX).),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) datatype related to Assessment, Performed.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with identifying ten-year probability of all major osteoporosis-related fracture as determined by the FRAX. This is a grouping of a SNOMED CT code.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
